{"tid":1939224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安倍：東京奧運如不能以完整形式舉行　或須推遲","createTime":"2020-03-23T04:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T05:09:44.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d940d7d9043594c948caf1e2b9fad75299f9fa5","tid":1939224,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"<del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">新型冠狀病毒</span></del><strong>武漢肺炎</strong>疫情愈見嚴峻，外界均關注原定7月24日揭幕的東京奧運能否如期舉行。日本一直堅持如期舉辦，但各界要求延期的壓力日增下，日本首相安倍晉三終於改口風。日本放送協會（NHK）今日（23日）報道，安倍今早在參議院預算委員會上表示，奧運如果無法以完整形式舉辦，可能不得不推遲，但仍稱不會考慮取消。<br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會（IOC）執委會周日（22日）亦召開了緊急會議，會後表示「取消東京奧運不在議程上」，現正研究延期，預計未來4星期會有決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200323/s00005/1584926291661/%e5%ae%89%e5%80%8d-%e6%9d%b1%e4%ba%ac%e5%a5%a7%e9%81%8b%e5%a6%82%e4%b8%8d%e8%83%bd%e4%bb%a5%e5%ae%8c%e6%95%b4%e5%bd%a2%e5%bc%8f%e8%88%89%e8%a1%8c-%e6%88%96%e9%a0%88%e6%8e%a8%e9%81%b2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200323%2Fs00005%2F1584926291661%2F%25e5%25ae%2589%25e5%2580%258d-%25e6%259d%25b1%25e4%25ba%25ac%25e5%25a5%25a7%25e9%2581%258b%25e5%25a6%2582%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%2583%25bd%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e5%25ae%258c%25e6%2595%25b4%25e5%25bd%25a2%25e5%25bc%258f%25e8%2588%2589%25e8%25a1%258c-%25e6%2588%2596%25e9%25a0%2588%25e6%258e%25a8%25e9%2581%25b2&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=a0129411\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200323%2Fs00005%2F1584926291661%2F%25e5%25ae%2589%25e5%2580%258d-%25e6%259d%25b1%25e4%25ba%25ac%25e5%25a5%25a7%25e9%2581%258b%25e5%25a6%2582%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%2583%25bd%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e5%25ae%258c%25e6%2595%25b4%25e5%25bd%25a2%25e5%25bc%258f%25e8%2588%2589%25e8%25a1%258c-%25e6%2588%2596%25e9%25a0%2588%25e6%258e%25a8%25e9%2581%25b2&h=2a53b437\" target=\"_blank\"